  "keyFeatures": [
    "Fully asynchronous using Python asyncio",
    "Decorator-based update handlers (on_message, on_updateNewMessage, etc.)",
    "Bound methods on TDLib types for ergonomic usage (message.reply_text, message.edit_text)",
    "Plugin system for modular bot architecture",
    "Built-in filter system for routing updates",
    "Support for both bot tokens and user accounts (userbot mode)",
    "RabbitMQ integration for horizontal scaling via TDLib Server",
    "Well-typed API wrapping the full TDLib surface"
  ],
